      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要设计一个带PWM调制的加权轮询仲裁器，用于监控总线。核心需求是支持N个请求源，每个源有独立的权重和信用额度管理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "arbiter_wrr_pwm_monbus",
        "Weighted Round-Robin",
        "Credit Management",
        "PWM Modulation"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。这个模块需要处理三类输入信号对吗？请求信号、数据本身，还有权重配置？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "req",
        "data",
        "weight",
        "Inputs"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，输入侧需要REQ、DATA和WEIGHT三组总线。REQ是N位的请求向量，DATA是N个64位数据包，WEIGHT是每个请求源的W位权重值。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "REQ",
        "DATA",
        "WEIGHT",
        "Monitor Bus Inputs"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我在左侧画了一个Monitor Bus Inputs的子图，里面放了req[N-1:0]、data[N-1:0][63:0]和weight[N-1:0][W-1:0]三个节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inputs",
        "REQ",
        "DATA",
        "WEIGHT"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "中间主体部分要分成四个功能块：WRR仲裁核心、信用管理、PWM控制器，以及输出选择器。信用管理要放在WRR前面做准入控制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Arbiter",
        "Credits",
        "PWM",
        "Mux",
        "arbiter_wrr_pwm_monbus"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
